            <h1>Introduction</h1>
            <p>Learn how to earn points by submitting your bus tickets and contributing to a greener planet.</p>

            <h1>How to Earn Points</h1>
            <p>You can earn points by submitting proof of your bus ticket usage. Each valid submission will reward you with points that contribute to your overall score.</p>

            <h1>Task Details</h1>
            <p>Each task listing includes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Description:</strong> Submit a photo of your bus ticket.</li>
                <li><strong>Points:</strong> The number of points awarded upon submission.</li>
                <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> Ongoing, submit as you go.</li>
                <li><strong>Steps:</strong> Take a clear photo of your bus ticket and upload it using the submission form.</li>
            </ul>

            <h1>Submitting Bus Tickets</h1>
            <p>To submit a bus ticket, upload a clear photo of it through the submission form below:</p>
            
            <h1>Upload File</h1>
            <p>You can upload your bus ticket proof here:</p>

            <form method = "POST" action"/getpoints" id="imageForm" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <input type="file" id="imageUpload" name = "ticket" accept="image/*" required>
            <button type="submit">Upload Image</button>
            </form>
            <div id="imagePreview"></div>
        </div>

